1. Valgrind Meamory leak check(Linux): Valgrind --leak-check=yes ./application_name
2. Give permission read write execute in a file to all its folders and files(linux): chmod -R 777 ./
3. Mannualy install boost on linux
  tar boost_1_58_0.tar.gz
  cd boost_1_58_0
  ./bootstrap.sh
  ./b2
Note: First install gcc and g++ if not installed.  
sudo apt install gcc
sudo apt install g++

4. Tcpdump command to check packets
tcpdump -i any -vv host 239.50.50.22  and port 10822

5. Install librabbitMq ubuntu
Step 1
sudo apt-get update -y
Step 2
sudo apt-get install -y librabbitmq-dev

6. To see working directory of a process having process ID(without dollar):
pwdx $pid
